I"«<p>Excellent article but it leaves off my favourite tip: Get a Mac. Use iPhoto, <a href="http://homepage.mac.com/kenferry/software.html">Keyword Assistant</a> and <a href="http://www.speirs.org/">Fraser Speirs</a>' awesome <a href="http://www.speirs.org/flickrexport/">FlickrExport</a>  plugin and go to Flickr heaven. No more chain of pain for uploading photos or tagging or creating photo sets. "Everything just works" (TM)!
</p>
